data.description: Owner maintained home with private backyard. Granite counters in kitchen and newer windows. Nice dining area. Both kitchen and primary bedroom open to patio. Large walk-in closet. Second bedroom has built-ins. 2 car detached garage with extra storage closets. Lots of space for your gardening ideas. Oakmont Village amenities include 2 golf courses, 3 recreation centers, tennis courts, picked ball courts, a bocce court, swimming pools, fitness center and so much more. Located in the heart of the Sonoma County Wine Country.
